etect buildings and commercial complexes constructed without approved plans or in violation of bylaws. This enforcement drive, focusing initially on major roads, aims to identify unauthorized land use changes and deviations from sanctioned layouts. Regular drone surveys will ensure ongoing monitoring and early detection of new violations.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/technology/lucknow-development-authority-uses-drones-to-crack-down-on-illegal-constructions/129590940?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-42608/129590940.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "technology"}]}